Ninja missions are tasks that can be done to unlock more <a href="/characters-and-skills/" class="con" title="characters">characters</a>.<br><br>
Step-by-step guide to do a mission:
<ul>
<li>1) Be the required rank or higher.</li>
<li>2) Have any required missions completed.</li>
<li>3) Press the <a href="/game-manual/" class="con" title="Start Playing">Start Playing</a> button.</li>
<li>4) Select any <a href="/characters-and-skills/" class="con" title="characters">characters</a> involved in any missions you wish to work on.</li>
<li>5) Play the <a href="/game-manual/" class="con" title="game">game</a> normally.</li>
<li>6) Finally understand that missions are not a seperate <a href="/game-manual/" class="con" title="game">game</a> but work in the background passively.</li>
</ul>

